oughout Europe as a model of a Christian king."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"John De Buhmley was born about 1270, in Ashton Under Lyne, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom. He married Mrs John De Buhmley before 1300, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died in 1336, at the age of 67."},"et":{"abt 1270–1336":"umbes 1270–1336","–Female":"Surnud","1300–1360":"1300–1360","1270–1336":"1270–1336","1336":"1336","before 1300":"enne 1300","1300":"1300","abt 1270":"umbes 1270","1360":"1360","1270":"1270","Ashton Under Lyne, Lancashire, England":"Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England","England":"England"},"fi":{"abt 1270–1336":"noin 1270–1336","–Female":"Kuollut","1300–1360":"1300–1360","1270–1336":"1270–1336","1336":"1336","before 1300":"ennen vuotta 1300","1300":"1300","abt 1270":"noin 1270","1360":"1360","1270":"1270","Ashton Under Lyne, Lancashire, England":"Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England","England":"England"},"fr":{"abt 1270–1336":"environ 1270–1336","–Female":"Décédée","1300–1360":"1300–1360","1270–1336":"1270–1336","1336":"1336","before 1300":"avant 1300","1300":"1300","abt 1270":"environ 1270","1360":"1360","1270":"1270","Ashton Under Lyne, Lancashire, England":"Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre","lifeSummary":"John De Buhmley est né environ 1270, à Ashton Under Lyne, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a épousé Mrs John De Buhmley avant 1300, à Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Il est décédé en 1336, à l’âge de 67 ans."},"de":{"abt 1270–1336":"um 1270–1336","–Female":"Verstorben","1300–1360":"1300–1360","1270–1336":"1270–1336","1336":"1336","before 1300":"vor 1300","1300":"1300","abt 1270":"um 1270","1360":"1360","1270":"1270","Ashton Under Lyne, Lancashire, England":"Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England","England":"England","lifeSummary":"John De Buhmley wurde um 1270 in Ashton Under Lyne, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hat vor 1300 in England Mrs John De Buhmley geheiratet. Sie hat